ion. Pre-fix dry-run mentioned in #501008 body but no post-fix run announced.\\n\\nIdempotency: YES (data-safe). target_skip_reason returns :customer_edit first if rf.updated_at \\u003e target.created_at+1min. After fix-run rewrites with NOW timestamps, re-runs skip as customer_edit. :already_restored check is technically unreachable post-run due to ordering.\\n\\nRecommended: dry_run=true via hammer rake in EU/AU/US — non-destructive, definitively answers.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"anubhav.bohidar@intercom.io\",\"created_at\":\"2026-04-27T10:31:27Z\",\"created_by\":\"anubhav-intercom\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-27T10:31:27Z\"}"}
